app, ss = basic_ss
test_client = SocketIOTestClient(app, ss.socketio, namespace=ss.namespace)
ss.subscription_manager.subscribe = Mock()
test_client.emit('message', json.dumps({'type': SUBSCRIPTION_START,
    'payload': 'foo', 'query': 'query test{ testString }', 'variables':
    'baz'}), namespace=ss.namespace)
ss.subscription_manager.subscribe.assert_called_once()
assert ss.subscription_manager.subscribe.call_args[1].get('callback', None
    ) != None
